              Hi! I am a data scientist, amateur economist, and a dabbling Bayesian. My academic background includes computer science, economics, and mathematics; my B.A. is from UC Santa Cruz and my M.S. is from Duke University.
              I am currently a data scientist at Modern Fertility.
